features: NATURALLY PURE: Experience the cleanest and greenest unscented wipes. Crafted from 100% naturally absorbent pulp and enriched with non-GMO, synthetic-free ingredients for optimal purity.
HYPOALLERGENIC: Dermatologically tested with a gentle formula and skin-nurturing ingredients to minimize irritation and allergic reactions.
FLUSHABLE & SAFE: Our wipes are INDA & EDANA compliant, feature rapid disintegration while maintaining impressive strength when wet. Safe for both sewers and septic systems.
ALOE VERA: Each baby wipe is enriched with soothing aloe vera, providing gentle care for your baby's sensitive skin.
NON-TOXIC: Our wipes are free from dyes, fragrances, optical brighteners, alcohol, chlorine, parabens, PET, and other detrimental chemicals.
body.description: Happy Little Campers natural baby wipes with aloe vera are non-toxic, fragrance free, alcohol free and chemical free to protect your newborn baby and toddlers sensitive skin. Our unscented hypoallergenic baby wipes are free from harmful chemicals and dyes and pure, gentle and safe for babies, toddlers and children. Ultra-soft and absorbent baby wipes for an easy, one-wipe clean. All Happy Little Camper wipes are free from animal origin ingredients.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Happy Little Camper Baby Wipes Pure, clean and ultra-soft baby wipes are perfect for on the go. Gentle for baby's sensitive skin. Happy Little Camper natural baby wipes with organic aloe vera are non-toxic, fragrance free, alcohol free and chemical free to protect your newborn baby and toddlers sensitive skin. Our unscented hypoallergenic baby wipes are free from harmful chemicals and dyes and pure, gentle and safe for babies, toddlers and children. Natural ultra-soft and thick baby wipes for an easy, one-wipe clean. HYPOALLERGENIC - dermatologically tested, gentle conditioning formula designed to reduce the risk of irritation or allergic reaction.ALOE VERA - protects your baby’s sensitive skin with ultra-soft wipes.NON-TOXIC - our products are free from dyes, fragrances, non-woven synthetics, alcohol, chlorine, parabens, PEGs and other harmful chemicals. Flushable Wipes WE LOVE NATURAL - Made from naturally absorbent 100% pulp, and our CLEAN SOLUTION we select the purest ingredients for our products.TOTALLY FLUSHABLE - Our Flushable wipes are INDA & EDANA compliant and feature rapid disintegration whilst maintaining excellent strength when wet. SEWER and SEPTIC SYSTEM SAFE. Natural Cotton Wipes WE LOVE NATURAL - Made from naturally absorbent GMO-free cotton, and our CLEAN SOLUTION we select the purest ingredients for our products.MOTHER NATURE APPROVED - we are committed to sustainable manufacturing practices, and packaging made from 40% recycled materials. We use 100% natural cotton, free of optical brighteners and totally chlorine free. All Happy Little Camper wipes are free from animal origin ingredients.

· Ideal for sensitive skin: Happy Little Camper water wipes are gentle enough for premature, newborn and infant skin · 100% All natural, plant based ingredients, with no nasties! · Super soft and Non-irritating · No chlorine, phthalates, parabens · Alcohol and Fragrance Free · Handy Flip-Top Lid Happy Little Camper Baby Wipes contain pure, natural, organic extracts to gently cleanse, soothe and care for your baby’s skin at change time. Happy Little Camper Water Wipes are not only perfect for baby, they can also be used as make up removers and are very handy to have in your home, car and hand bag too.

About Happy Little Camper When it comes to the Happy Little Camper in our lives, natural is better, which is why we’ve created baby products that are naturally safe and naturally better for your baby's skin and for the environment.​ This means that not only is your baby comfortable in Happy Little Camper, but also safe and free from harsh chemicals. Knowing the facts, consider making a better choice for your baby’s bottom by making Happy Little Camper your go-to natural baby care brand. We're committed to sustainably - sourced ingredients, safe manufacturing processes and packaging made from recycled materials.
GMO-Free Natural Cotton Baby Wipes Hypoallergenic Baby Wipes Soothing Aloe Vera and Vitamin E Baby Wipes Ultra-Absorbent Baby Wipes

Plant-Based, Natural Baby Care Products Made from 100% natural cotton, our products contain pure and healthy ingredients. All Happy Little Camper wipes are free from animal origin ingredients. Products You Can Count On Our 100% natural cotton wipes are fragrance-free and paraben-free. Natural Baby Care at Affordable Prices We never use any of the nasty chemicals conventional brands use, because we wouldn't sell products we wouldn't be confident to use on our own happy little campers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really like these wipes
reviews.reviewText: Great wipes, perfect for sensitive skin. They are sometimes hard to get out of the package though. I think they are a bit expensive too but I still buy them as they work well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 7, 2020
reviews.reviewText: Just what I was searching for---safe yet effective wipes. The size and thickness of these make them especially useful. They're not too wet nor are they too dry. Love they have no fragrance & are not full of chemicals. Will purchase again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 15, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Works well, doesn’t clog toilet, could be “wetter”
reviews.reviewText: These wipes work well and are great for sensitive skin. They don’t clog the toilet at all. I dislike that they can be difficult to get out of the container and they aren’t as wet as I would like them to be. They will dry out very fast of the cover isn’t kept closed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 27, 2018
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Happy paws, tooshies, and toilets!
reviews.reviewText: These are the only minimal-ingredient wet wipes that are point blankly flushable. I used to use the Honest Co. wipes, but I suspected they weren’t supposed to be flushed, even though nothing on the package stated otherwise. I decided to reprieve my septic system and try Happy Little Camper, and I’ve fully switched over to these wipes.They’re a good size for adult and dog-paw use, and I’ve never had issues with them tearing in either situation. Although I wish they were a little more wet, the peace of mind for my septic system is worth it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 16, 2020
reviews.reviewText: I like that the wipes come a bit dry because I add filtered water to the package and let it sit overnight. Let me tell ya, they turn out perfect. They’re amazing for cleaning doggy paws.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: They’re ok. I got them to aid the potty training process. I like that they’re mild for sensitive skin, however they are very easy to tear, which isn’t great for wiping an antsy toddler tush.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 29, 2021
reviews.reviewText: Awesome. And no weird smell like other brands! Thick material and doesn’t easily tear or crumble. Doesn’t irritate highly sensitive skin. Definitely will buy again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best wipes ever
reviews.reviewText: These are the best wipes I’ve ever used, by far.

Absolutely LOVED these wipes! The whole family used them on our recent trip to the cottage and we are all in agreement that these are the best! We used them for the kids sticky faces/hands, in the washroom along with toilet paper and I even used them for cleaning my face and armpits to feel refreshed! They left no residue, the scent is light and they are durable. Will definitely purchase these again!

reviews.reviewText: Very happy with the product. Good value for money and do the job.
Fantastic. It is made from paper and does a good job wiping. Mild to no scent.
Great size sturdy, they don’t just disintegrate into nothing. Don’t dry up. Delivery spot on!
